==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Boza
<hw>Bo"za</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Bosa</er>.]</ety> <def>An acidulated fermented drink of the Arabs
and Egyptians, made from millet seed and various astringent substances;
also, an intoxicating beverage made from hemp seed, darnel meal, and
water.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>bosa</asp>, <asp>bozah</asp>,
<asp>bouza</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

